# description
This project has three branches.

The first branch is the master branch. It contains our UI design and creates HTML and CSS.

The second branch is mongo_mongoose. It contains the backend part and uses Mongoose and Node.js. In order to use this branch, you need to install the Mongoose package and other required packages. This part uses a local MongoDB.

The third branch is mysql. It contains the backend part and the MySQL database part. To use this branch, you need to install the MySQL package. The project's MySQL server is created using WampServer.
